<div>
    <h2>Application Procedure</h2>
    <p>
        STEP 1: Register your account and activate it.<br />
        STEP 2: Fill out the “Application Form of Liaoning Shihua University of the People’s Republic of China”and upload all required documents as follows:<br />
        <ul>
            <li>a.Provide academic credentials of the highest level （Notarized English translation if applicable).</li>
            <li>b.Provide your final degree transcript （Notarized English translation if applicable.</li>
            <li>c.Provide the copy of all pages of passport. (From the first page to last one)</li>
            <li>d.Provide a passport photo.</li>
            <li>e.Provide Physical Examination Record for Foreigners (Within 3 months).</li>
            <li>f.Provide letter of sponsorship (download). g.Provide the transfer letter and transcript (transfer student only)</li>
            <li>h.Provide the HSK certificate (for Chinese-Medium programs only)</li>
            <li>i.Provide recommendation letters from at least two different professors(master programs only).</li>
        </ul>
        STEP 3: Submit the application and note your application number.<br />
        STEP 4: Check your admission status regularly.<br />
        STEP 5: You will get message through the on-line application system after successful verification.<br />
        STEP 6: Check your message and after your documents are qualified, please pay for Application Fee: 800 RMB and do upload the receipt.<br />
        PS: Application  fee is non-refundable.  Please check LSHU bank account details below.<br />
        STEP 7: Wait for the foreign affairs office to approve JW202 (usually takes 10-15 days).<br />
        STEP 8: Receive originals of “Admission notice” and “JW202” by post.<br />
        STEP 9: Apply for VISA
    </p>
</div>

