        TIPS FOR FASTER AND SUCCESSFUL ADMISSION<br />
        <ol>
            <li>Always mention your online application number when making enquiries with us.</li>
            <li>Your CV must be complete & continuous until the current year. (Study or work experience)</li>
            <li>Ensure all information and documents submitted/uploaded are factual and legible.</li>
            <li>All applications will be verified within 3 working days.</li>
            <li>After checking the application documents and receiving application fee, our university will submit related documents to Liaoning Provincial Government to apply for the “Application Form for Foreigners Wishing to Study in China”, i.e. JW202.</li>
            <li>After the JW202 is successfully applied,our university will send the admission letter and JW202 to the applicants.</li>
            <li>Applicants who are admitted should register at International Education College of Liaoning Shihua University with the original copies of application documents before the regulated time in the admission letter.If the students are not able to register for some reasonable excuses, they should notify the university beforehand, otherwise we will cancel their admission qualifications.</li>
